n Hours, Film Series, and special events by clicking on the tabs below.         What's happening at LCLC:   What's happening at LCLC:         Involvement Fair Spring 2020       Go to slide 1    Go to slide 2    Go to slide 3    Go to slide 4    Go to slide 5    Go to slide 6    Go to slide 7    Go to slide 8    Go to slide 9    Go to slide 10                Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                 Go to the next slide    Go to the previous slide                  Schedules of Events and Peer Tutoring            Peer Tutoring (click for more)  Language Events (click for more)  For Instructors (click for more)      Peer Tutoring in Italian, French, German, and Spanish  LCLC now offers free Peer Tutoring in 301 Grant Hall for all BLP students in French, German, Italian, and Spanish. Click below for schedules.      Peer Tutoring           French Peer Tutoring  Click here to see the schedule of French Peer Tutoring             Italian Peer Tutoring  Click here to see the schedule of Italian Peer Tutoring             German Peer Tutoring  Click here to see the schedule of German Peer Tutoring             Spanish Peer Tutoring  Click here to see the schedule of Spanish Peer Tutoring            Schedules of Language Events  LCLC offers various language events happening in our Language Oasis (GH 308). See the schedules for Conversation Hours, Film Series, and other events!      Language Events           Conversation Hours  Click here to see t